	<h1 class="title">推荐电影《史蒂夫·乔布斯》，一部丰富而强大的时代纪录</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">A.O.Scott</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-10 12:05:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15868/medium/15868.jpg?1444394534" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


